snippet.title: Air Havoc Controller - video component
snippet.description:
More weird stuff I found on my Hive CD. A game called Air Havoc Controller, where you presumably play as an air traffic controller. I don't know though because I can't install the game, I can only access these videos. Does anyone know anything about this game? Like Magzone, it is a complete mystery to me. Sorry if the video gets a bit boring after a while, it just turns into planes taxiing away from the terminals.

Air Havoc Controller belongs to Trimark Interactive. Like my other videos, this serves as a way to celebrate these old games and document them before our computers become so advanced they may never be playable or watchable again.
